io.elegie.luchess.pgn.api

Class AbstractParserVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elegie.luchess.pgn.api.AbstractParserVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GameBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractParserVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParserVisitor
    This is a convenience class providing an empty implementation for all methods of the ParserVisitor interface. Inherited classes only need to override the methods they are interested into.
